## Kick ##

#showtooltip [nostance:2] Pummel; Shield Bash
/startattack
/cast [noworn:shield,nostance:3] Berserker Stance
/cast [@mouseover,harm,stance:3][stance:3] Pummel
/cast [stance:2,worn:shield] Shield Bash
